rComments: This was supposed to be an easy class for beginners/intermediate. But it turned out to be the WORST class I've ever taken. Her exams are SO CONFUSING, she made us retake an exam cause the first one was a mess! The level of difficulty doesn't reflect at all what you do in class. And her classes are so BORING. Advice: DON'T TAKE this class with her!

The worst class I've ever taken! She is super monotone! The classes are super boring!!!!!She requires a textbook but the book is really useless. I don't think I learn things from the class. Avoid as possible.
